{
  "stem": "27509.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The music was playing for lunch, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- as the saying goes, 'The house burns, and the-- and the clock ticks.' And so the absurdities, the contradictions were everywhere, everywhere, everywhere, in terms of, of social behavior and interactions, and so on, as if nothing has happened, as if nothing-- and yet, the, the, the ground was removed from, from everybody's-- under their feet.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, but the behavioral patterns were so ingrained and so, and so kept to, to give some sort of semblance of normality of maybe a, a, a, a, a form of self-assurance that you are still a human being.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is still some sort of a dignity left in your personality, and so on, hoping that maybe, maybe day after tomorrow may not be as tragic and as-- as it turned out to be.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A year.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I stayed there a year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But here comes into play the famous historical fact that turned out to be a savior for a few thousand people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a case of a Dutch rabbinical student who studied at a yeshiva in Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was caught in the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he ran, together with his entire yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was the [INAUDIBLE] Yeshiva-- 400 rabbinical students ran.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The entire yeshiva, with their rabbis, with their managers, with their-- the entire thing went to Wilno.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this man-- who was not a Polish citizen; he was a Dutch citizen-- wanted to find a way how to get to Holland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, the western way, you couldn't because by that time, France and Holland was occupied, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He went-- he went to see the Dutch consulate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Dutch consulate gave him a visa to Curacao.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Curacao was a, a, a, a Dutch protectorate.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
